    • printStudentInfo

      public void printStudentInfo(int option)
      Given a concrete Student (this), the function prints by screen the Student info as required by the parameter option.
      Parameters:
      option - - The option requiring the info to print.
      If option = 1, the function prints the Student name.
      If option = 2, the function prints the Student ID.
      If option = 3, the function prints "Thank you for joining the Programming Society" if the student is a member of the programming society. Otherwise it prints "Please consider joining the Programming Society".
      If option different from 1, 2 and 3, then the function does not print anything.

    • sumOfIDDigits

      The sum of the digits of its ID.
